"{\"uid\": \"thestar.com-news-morning-digest-canadas-on-an-olympic-gold-rush-for-profit-health-care-creeping-across-canada-article_90e7a4d2-4e62-11ef-a0b4-1f783343321a.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"        Team Canada raking in the Olympic hardware, doctors standing against for-profit health care and a hard look at Canada's airline industry.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 119, \"end\": 125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.739322491431315e-14, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team Canada raking in the Olympic hardware, doctors standing against for-profit health care and a hard look at Canada's airline industry.\", \"from\": 147, \"to\": 284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 147, \"end\": 158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hockey_Canada\", \"score\": 0.5515125938339108, \"rank\": 0.8131069285224628, \"text\": \"Team Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hockey_Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hockey_Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 258, \"end\": 264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.739322491431315e-14, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gold medalist Christa Deguchi of Team Canada poses for a photo with their medal on the podium during the Judo Women's 57kg medal ceremony on day three of the Paris Olympic games.\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 464, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 300, \"end\": 315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christa_Deguchi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Christa Deguchi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christa_Deguchi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christa_Deguchi\"}, {\"begin\": 319, \"end\": 330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hockey_Canada\", \"score\": 0.5515125938339108, \"rank\": 0.8131069285224628, \"text\": \"Team Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hockey_Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hockey_Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Good morning.\", \"from\": 466, \"to\": 479, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the Tuesday, July 30 edition of First Up, the Star's daily morning digest.Sign up to get it earlier each day, in your inbox.\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 612, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's the latest on Team Canada raking in theOlympic hardware, for-profithealth carecreeping across the nation and a probe intoCanada's airline industry.\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 768, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 635, \"end\": 646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hockey_Canada\", \"score\": 0.5515125938339108, \"rank\": 0.8131069285224628, \"text\": \"Team Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hockey_Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hockey_Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meet Christa Deguchi, the 28-year-old phenom who gripped, locked and ankle-hooked her way to Canada's very first gold in judo, Rosie DiManno writes - the country's first gold at the Paris Olympics, too.\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 972, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 863, \"end\": 869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.739322491431315e-14, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 897, \"end\": 902, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosie_M._Banks\", \"score\": 0.9906226455952357, \"rank\": 0.009396650535587381, \"text\": \"Rosie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosie_M._Banks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosie_M._Banks\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's despite a hissing and hollering French crowd, who heckled as she came out on top against France's Sarah-L\\u00e9onie Cysique in the semifinals.\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 1117, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1012, \"end\": 1018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9806818189850455, \"rank\": 0.01954542928118014, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1069, \"end\": 1075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999852259243182, \"rank\": 6.92521783811908e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1078, \"end\": 1098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah-L\\u00e9onie_Cysique\", \"score\": 0.9999999999349711, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sarah-L\\u00e9onie Cysique\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah-L\\u00e9onie_Cysique\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah-L\\u00e9onie_Cysique\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Deguchi was unswayed, confronting and toppling the reigning world champion, Korea's Mi-Mi Huh, in the shadow of the Eiffel Tower yesterday.Here's what she had to say following her historic win.\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1315, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1198, \"end\": 1203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.947086056304192, \"rank\": 0.05450927076304265, \"text\": \"Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As for-profit practices gradually seep into Canada's public health care system, a group of doctors from across the nation are stepping up to fight back.\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1361, \"end\": 1367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.739322491431315e-14, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Canadian Medical Association is calling on governments to ensure medically necessary care is based on need, not the ability to pay.\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1605, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1474, \"end\": 1502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Medical_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Canadian Medical Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Medical_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Medical_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Health care should not privilege those who can afford to pay for services,\\\" one doctor tells Allan Woods.Privatization is not inevitable; look at the doctors' recommendations and what they are fighting for.\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1813, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Amid a rising tide of traveller complaints about the cost and quality of services, Canada's Competition Bureau is taking a hard look at the nation's airline industry, Josh Rubin reports.\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 2001, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1898, \"end\": 1904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.739322491431315e-14, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 1907, \"end\": 1925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Competition_Bureau\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Competition Bureau\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Competition_Bureau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Competition_Bureau\"}, {\"begin\": 1982, \"end\": 1986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9721230647051847, \"rank\": 0.02857939184559845, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time, following changes to the federal Competition Act, they have come armed with new powers - like the ability to demand documents from companies.\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2154, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The only two entities who benefit from the current situation are Air Canada and WestJet, not the travelling public,\\\" said Flair Airlines' interim CEO.But will the bureau actually use their new powers?\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2356, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2221, \"end\": 2231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_Canada\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Air Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 2236, \"end\": 2243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WestJet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WestJet\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WestJet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WestJet\"}, {\"begin\": 2278, \"end\": 2292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flair_Airlines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Flair Airlines\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flair_Airlines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flair_Airlines\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Deputy Prime Minister and Minister of Finance Chrystia Freeland stands next to Prime Minister Justin Trudeau as she speaks to employees during a visit to a Toronto Transit Commission yard in Toronto.\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2557, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2452, \"end\": 2466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Trudeau\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Justin Trudeau\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Trudeau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Trudeau\"}, {\"begin\": 2514, \"end\": 2540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto_Transit_Commission\", \"score\": 0.9999999996625775, \"rank\": 3.375157553961415e-10, \"text\": \"Toronto Transit Commission\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto_Transit_Commission\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto_Transit_Commission\"}, {\"begin\": 2549, \"end\": 2556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.203715614239828e-19, \"text\": \"Toronto\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This Olympic hot spot is giving the Eiffel Tower and Louvre some competition.\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2636, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2612, \"end\": 2618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre_Palace\", \"score\": 0.6562323899350975, \"rank\": 0.5238504153979787, \"text\": \"Louvre\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre_Palace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre_Palace\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Canadian politicians bicker between half-measures and nothing at all, other countries are pursuing ambitious plans that could fundamentally remake their digital economies and save their news industries, Justin Ling writes.\", \"from\": 2638, \"to\": 2863, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2641, \"end\": 2649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999764753335922, \"rank\": 2.3522549521712317e-05, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The continued heat encouraged many to head to Woodbine Beach to keep cool and have fun on Monday.\", \"from\": 2865, \"to\": 2962, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2911, \"end\": 2925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodbine_Beach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Woodbine Beach\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodbine_Beach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodbine_Beach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"WOODBINE BEACH:Beachgoers were living their best lives at Woodbine Beach Monday, soaking up the sun and warm weather.\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 3081, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's shaping up to be a warm week, with a smattering of clouds and possible rain.Here's how the forecast is looking.\", \"from\": 3082, \"to\": 3198, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you for reading First Up.\", \"from\": 3200, \"to\": 3231, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can reach me and the First Up team atfirstup@thestar.ca  Sign up hereto get this newsletter in your inbox.\", \"from\": 3232, \"to\": 3342, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kevin Jiang is a Toronto-based staff reporter for the Star's Express Desk.\", \"from\": 3344, \"to\": 3418, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Reach him at:kjiang@thestar.ca  Error!There was an error processing your request.\", \"from\": 3419, \"to\": 3500, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There was a problem with the recaptcha.\", \"from\": 3502, \"to\": 3541, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please try again.\", \"from\": 3542, \"to\": 3559, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You may unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 3561, \"to\": 3593, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By signing up, you agree to ourterms of useandprivacy policy.\", \"from\": 3594, \"to\": 3655, \"entities\": []}, {\"sent